            "title": "革命尚未成功 圖達通還要努力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/soW8hlXrFtFgEgWMdMujyw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/the_bamboo_works_186/7bcd5b72fe0385b74bc6ecc17ecea9d4\" width=\"500\"/></div></figure></div>",
