        {
            "title": "高盛雙級上調挪威海德魯評級,供應順風助力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5vjETd.FYP4tf6NUlq38Uw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEE39198_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 高盛將挪威海德魯(<span><span>Norsk Hydro</span></span>)評級從\"賣出\"雙級上調至\"買入\",理由是盈利前景改善以及高附加值鋁產品供應環境更加有利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該券商將12個月目標價從69挪威克朗上調至120挪威克朗,指出下游鋁市場的定價假設更強勁,溢價更高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">挪威海德魯股價近期上漲,在3月和4月初穩步攀升後,觸及審查期間的最高水平。截至美國東部時間07:50(格林威治標準時間11:50),該股上漲4.8%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-27bb5b42-2119-3aac-9678-11265069eb82-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛表示,與中東地區中斷相關的供應衝擊可能會收緊高附加值產品的供應,這些產品用於汽車和航空航天等板塊。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該券商估計,此次中斷可能會削減約16%的中國以外高附加值鋁供應,使市場動態從價格主導轉向供應主導。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">挪威海德魯是歐洲最大的綜合鋁生產商之一,因其在高利潤率下游產品方面的敞口而被視為處於有利地位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據報告,其約70-75%的產量為高附加值產品,其中約60%銷往歐洲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛還上調了盈利預測,預計2026年每股收益為9.47挪威克朗,較先前估計大幅上升,受到更高鋁價和溢價上升的支撐。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該券商指出,儘管需求狀況仍不確定,尤其是在下游板塊,但供應限制可能會支撐近期盈利動能。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛補充說,挪威海德魯的綜合運營、既有客戶關係和計劃中的產能提升可能有助於其比同行更好地應對當前市場環境。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛表示,前景面臨的風險包括鋁價低於預期、成本通脹以及下游需求持續疲軟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E9%9B%99%E7%B4%9A%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E6%B5%B7%E5%BE%B7%E9%AD%AF%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E9%A0%86%E9%A2%A8%E5%8A%A9%E5%8A%9B-125007434.html",
